  "description": "[Description]",
  "readme_markdown": "<h2><a id=\"user-content-description\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#description\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z\"></path></svg></a>[Description]</h2>\n<p>Easily customize your server.</p>\n<p>By installing this plugin you will be able to customize your server MOTD.</p>\n<p>Add unlimate & colorful & changeable MOTD for your server.</p>\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-usage\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#usage\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z\"></path></svg></a>[Setup]</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Put phar from Poggit into <code>plugins</code> folder</li>\n<li>Edit the Settings.yml file of plugin in <code>plugin_data/RandomMOTD</code></li>\n  <li>you can disable or enable plugin by set <code>start-working: </code> to false or true</li>\n  <li>You can set colorful messages in Settings.yml</li>\n  <li>You can change RepeatTime of MOTD in Settings.yml</li>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Hope you enjoy using plugin.<p>",
